                                <li>List books you want to sell, find books you need.</li>
                                <li>Promote your own textbook Selling Page.</li>
                                <li>Meet on-campus to do the deal.</li>
                                <li>Interact directly with students. Pay cash.</li>
                                <li>No shipping. No credit cards.</li>
                                <li>Use the online textbook price comparison.</li>
                                <li>IT'S TOTALLY FREE!</li>
                                <li>Check out the 2 minute "How it Works":<br/>
                                    <a style="color:#147DB4; text-decoration: underline" href="http://localhost:8080/Student2StudentApp/app/#/conceptVideo">Watch Now!</a></li>
                            </ul>
