                            <p >... tell your friends, tell your classmates, tell the world... the more members we get, the more everyone will SAVE!</p>
                            <p >It's time to take back the bookstore! Cutout the middleman and spend your money on something better!!! Or do you like to get ripped-off?</p>

                            <text >
                                Cheers,<br/>
                                {{fullName}}<br/>
                                <a style="color:#147DB4;text-decoration: none">{{email}}</a>
                            </text>


                        </td>
                        <td width="35%" valign="top" align="center" style="width:40%;padding:10px; font-size:14px;color:#147DB4">
                            <br/><br/>
                            <a href="http://student2student.com/signup"><img src="{{ join_button }}"/></a><br/><br/>
                            <p style="font-style: italic;" >Personal Message for you:</p><br/>
                            <text>{{message}}</text>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center">
                            <img src="{{ share_image }}" alt="Student2student main hero image" width="600" height="136" style="display:block" title="Student2student main hero image">
